summary: Adds a new player home to the area around the Riverwood. Comes with a fast travel marker, no need to discover it. Has all crafting stations except smelter, shrine of Talos, and an air duct system.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a new player home to the area around the Riverwood. Comes with a fast travel marker, no need to discover it. Has all crafting stations except smelter, shrine of Talos, and an air duct system. Has four rooms: a bedroom, a dining room, a living room, and a crafting room. Air duct system links to all four rooms, while the central \"unit\" is located in the main/living room.
Hope you enjoy, please leave constructive criticism or positive feedback!
Not compatible with any mods that modify the UnownedCell cell, or that modify Tamriel coordinates X 3, Y -11.
author: COLE TRAIN
